    "For triplets that are incorrectly formatted, we discard them using regular expressions.",
    "For triplets that fail to capture toxic semantics, we urge the LLM to filter out non-toxic triplets with few-shot prompting, ensuring that only those triplets capable of evoking hatred and toxicity are retained.",
